Emacs X Window Manager (aka EXWM) is an Emacs tiling window manager for X11,
built on top of [https://github.com/ch11ng/xelb XELB] (the X protocol
Emacs Lisp Binding).

The current version of EXWM is
[https://github.com/emacs-exwm/exwm/releases/tag/0.34 0.34 released on
2025-06-27].

EXWM is [https://github.com/emacs-exwm/exwm developed on Github].

There is also a [https://github.com/emacs-exwm/exwm/wiki wiki for EXWM on
Github].

